'''Needa''' may refer to:
*[[Dame Needa]], a performing artist
*[[Lorth Needa/Legends|Lorth Needa]], [[Imperial Navy/Legends|Imperial Navy]] officer and [[Captain/Legends|captain]] of the [[Avenger/Legends|''Avenger'']]
*[[Needa (lieutenant)|Needa]], a [[Lieutenant/Legends|lieutenant]] in the [[Sith Empire (Post–Great Hyperspace War)|Sith Empire]]
*[[Virar Needa]], cousin of Lorth Needa, an Imperial lieutenant on an [[Orbital Solar Energy Transfer Satellite]] above [[Coruscant/Legends|Coruscant]]

